thread.title: Peter Selar
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Peter Selar

author: Peter Selar
title: Peter Selar
text: Shannon has been managing my/our properties for some years and I am very happy with this relationship. Shannon is proactive and provides great communication and follow up. I am confident that as Shannon presents to the landlord, she also presents to the tenant. This consistency in quality service delivery engenders trust I have in this individual and the extended Nelson Alexander (nee McLaren) team.
